PROJECT TITLE: 04.06 Writing Text Files 

PURPOSE OF PROJECT: The purpose of this project is to simulate trials until a particular animal is spotted by writing a text file(s). 

VERSION or DATE: 2/07/2021

HOW TO START THIS PROJECT: We use for loops and if statements to ensure the user's input is correct/setting the number of trials. 

AUTHORS: Trisha Ganesh 

USER INSTRUCTIONS:

This project allows you to write a text file as well as use concepts from 4.03 
